====================================================================

Layer                    Owner
-----------------------------------------
Public IP                GKE
TLS termination           GKE or Istio
Routing                  Istio
Security                 Istio
Observability             Envoy
Retries / Timeouts        Envoy
Canary / Blue-Green       Envoy


